lead_paragraph: Arsenal midfielder Alexis Sanchez has suffered a muscle injury and will miss Chile's World Cup qualifier against Colombia, the Chilean Football Federation said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Arsenal's Sanchez Out of Chile Qualifier With Muscle Strain
